    </p>

    <section class="project-card" aria-labelledby="project-geosound">
      <h2 id="project-geosound">Geosound</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Technologies:</strong> Node.js, Express, MongoDB, Mongoose,
        RESTful APIs.
      </p>
      <p>
        A platform where blind pupils can study geography in an accessible and
        engaging way. I built this platform with the help of Copilot to test the
        vibe of coding—whether it can really produce something production-ready.
        It was created for a student as part of her graduation project in the
        field of education.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/bassem-krayem/geosound"
